{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "adsmagic-messaging-api-2025",
		"name": "📱 Messaging API - UAZAPI & Endpoints",
		"description": "Collection completa para testar mensageria: criação de instância UAZAPI e todos os endpoints de mensageria\n\n**✅ Endpoint Unificado de Conexão:**\n- POST /messaging/connect/:accountId - Conecta instância ao WhatsApp (QR Code ou Pair Code via body)\n  - Body vazio `{}`: Gera QR Code (expira em 2 minutos)\n  - Body com `{\"phone\": \"...\"}`: Gera Pair Code (expira em 5 minutos)\n\n**⚠️ Endpoints Removidos (versão 0.6.0):**\n- ❌ GET /messaging/qrcode/:accountId - REMOVIDO (use POST /connect com body vazio)\n- ❌ GET /messaging/paircode/:accountId - REMOVIDO (use POST /connect com phone no body)\n\n**📝 Nota:** Esta collection foi atualizada após refatoração completa dos handlers de conexão.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "adsmagic-messaging"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "🔧 UAZAPI - Gerenciamento de Instância",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Criar Instância UAZAPI",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    const instanceName = response.instance?.instanceName || response.instanceName;",
									"    const apikey = response.instance?.apikey || response.apikey;",
									"    ",
									"    if (instanceName) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"uazapi_instance_id\", instanceName);",
									"        console.log(\"✅ Instância criada:\", instanceName);",
									"    }",
									"    ",
									"    if (apikey) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"uazapi_apikey\", apikey);",
									"        console.log(\"✅ API Key obtida\");",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							},
							{
								"key": "admintoken",
								"value": "{{uazapi_master_apikey}}",
								"type": "text",
								"description": "Admin Token da UAZAPI (obtenha na sua conta UAZAPI)",
								"disabled": false
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"{{uazapi_instance_name}}\",\n  \"systemName\": \"apilocal\",\n  \"adminField01\": \"custom-metadata-1\",\n  \"adminField02\": \"custom-metadata-2\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{uazapi_url}}/instance/init",
							"host": [
								"{{uazapi_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"instance",
								"init"
							]
						},
						"description": "Cria uma nova instância na UAZAPI\n\n**⚠️ AUTENTICAÇÃO NECESSÁRIA:**\nEste endpoint requer autenticação. Você precisa:\n1. Criar uma conta na UAZAPI: https://uazapi.com\n2. Obter seu Admin Token no painel\n3. Configurar a variável `uazapi_master_apikey` no Environment\n\n**Header de Autenticação:**\n- `admintoken`: Seu Admin Token da UAZAPI\n\n**Documentação:** https://docs.uazapi.com/\n\n**Resposta esperada:**\n```json\n{\n  \"instance\": {\n    \"instanceName\": \"minha-instancia\",\n    \"apikey\": \"...\",\n    \"token\": \"...\"\n  }\n}\n```"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Conectar Instância (Gerar QR Code)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test(\"Response has QR Code\", function () {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    const qrCode = response.qrcode?.base64 || response.qrcode?.qr || response.base64 || response.qr;",
									"    pm.expect(qrCode).to.exist;",
									"});",
									"",
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    console.log(\"✅ QR Code gerado com sucesso!\");",
									"    console.log(\"📱 Escaneie o QR Code com seu WhatsApp\");",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							},
							{
								"key": "admintoken",
								"value": "{{uazapi_apikey}}",
								"type": "text",
								"description": "Admin Token da UAZAPI"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{messaging_phone_to}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{uazapi_url}}/instance/connect",
							"host": [
								"{{uazapi_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"instance",
								"connect"
							]
						},
						"description": "Conecta a instância ao WhatsApp gerando QR Code\n\n**Header de Autenticação:**\n- `admintoken`: Admin Token da UAZAPI\n\n**Documentação:** https://docs.uazapi.com/\n\n**Body opcional:** Campo `phone` é opcional\n\n**Resposta esperada:**\n```json\n{\n  \"qrcode\": {\n    \"base64\": \"data:image/png;base64,...\",\n    \"code\": \"...\"\n  }\n}\n```"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Endpoints diretos da API UAZAPI para gerenciamento de instâncias"
		},
		{
			"name": "📝 Messaging - Criar Instância e Salvar",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Criar Instância UAZAPI (Salva no Banco)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test(\"Status code is 201\", function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test(\"Instance created and saved\", function () {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('success');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('accountId');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('instanceName');",
									"});",
									"",
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    ",
									"    if (jsonData.data.accountId) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"messaging_account_id\", jsonData.data.accountId);",
									"        console.log(\"✅ Conta criada no banco:\", jsonData.data.accountId);",
									"    }",
									"    ",
									"    if (jsonData.data.instanceName) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"uazapi_instance_id\", jsonData.data.instanceName);",
									"        console.log(\"✅ Instância criada:\", jsonData.data.instanceName);",
									"    }",
									"    ",
									"    if (jsonData.data.apikey) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"uazapi_apikey\", jsonData.data.apikey);",
									"        console.log(\"✅ API Key salva\");",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{
									"key": "token",
									"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"projectId\": \"{{project_id}}\",\n  \"instanceName\": \"{{uazapi_instance_name}}\",\n  \"adminToken\": \"{{uazapi_master_apikey}}\",\n  \"apiBaseUrl\": \"{{uazapi_url}}\",\n  \"systemName\": \"apilocal\",\n  \"accountName\": \"Conta WhatsApp UAZAPI\",\n  \"phone\": \"{{messaging_phone_to}}\",\n  \"adminField01\": \"custom-metadata-1\",\n  \"adminField02\": \"custom-metadata-2\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{functions_url}}/messaging/instances/uazapi",
							"host": [
								"{{functions_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"messaging",
								"instances",
								"uazapi"
							]
						},
						"description": "Cria uma instância na UAZAPI e salva automaticamente no banco de dados\n\n**O que este endpoint faz:**\n1. Cria instância na UAZAPI usando o Admin Token\n2. Salva automaticamente no banco (tabela `messaging_accounts`)\n3. Retorna os dados da conta criada\n\n**Campos obrigatórios:**\n- `projectId`: UUID do projeto\n- `instanceName`: Nome da instância\n- `adminToken`: Admin Token da UAZAPI\n\n**Campos opcionais:**\n- `apiBaseUrl`: URL base da API (padrão: https://free.uazapi.com)\n- `systemName`: Nome do sistema (padrão: apilocal)\n- `phone`: Número de telefone\n- `accountName`: Nome da conta\n- `adminField01`, `adminField02`: Campos customizados\n\n**Resposta:**\n- `accountId`: ID da conta criada no banco\n- `instanceName`: Nome da instância\n- `apikey`: API Key da instância\n- `account`: Dados da conta criada"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Endpoint da nossa API que cria instância e salva no banco automaticamente"
		},
		{
			"name": "📨 Messaging - Webhooks",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Webhook - UAZAPI",
